                {% elsif page.handle == 'result-hinglish' %} 
                <p>Surgery body ko stress me daalti hai jisse hair loss ho sakta hai. Surgery ke time pe jo dawaai diye jaate hai, usse bhi hair loss ho sakta hai. Aise time par, bhukhe rehne se aur diet mein rok-tok ki wajah se baalo ke health pe asar padta hai.</p>
                {% else %}
                <p>Surgery can stress the body and cause hair loss. Anesthesia and medications used during surgery may have side effects, including hair loss. Fasting and dietary restrictions before or after the surgery can also affect hair health.</p>
                {% endif %}
